CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1969 reads: " Lovely Paulette Butler, a new model on the sophisticated scene, wore for the Symphony Society Fashion Gala's finale, and Oscar de la Renta Velvet and brilliant gown with long tight sleeves and a pearl choker."--Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Paulette Butler modeling Oscar de la Renta gown with triangular patterned skirt and set of beaded chokers, posed on stage at the Symphony Society Gala.
